#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acquiring Screenshots"
msgstr "Dobijanje Screenshotova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <quote>screenshot</quote> is a snapshot of what is on your computer's "
"screen. It can be useful to explain some actions that should be done to "
"obtain the result, or to show the issue that you have found."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Screenshot</quote> je slika onog što je na zaslonu vašeg računara. "
"Može biti korisno za objašnjavanje nekih akcija koje bi trebalo uraditi za "
"dobijanje rezultate ili pokazivanje problema na koji ste naišli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make screenshot ready for editing in &kolourpaint; window you can use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Acquire Screenshot</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> item from &kolourpaint; main menu."
msgstr ""
"Da biste screenchot učinili spremnim za uređivanje u prozoru &kolourpaint;-a "
"možete koristiti <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Napravi screenshot</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Using the opened dialog you can change <guilabel>Screenshot Delay</"
#| "guilabel> (in seconds), and choose to <guilabel>Hide Main Window</"
#| "guilabel> during screenshoting. When you are ready to take screenshot "
#| "just click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The screenshot taken will be placed "
#| "directly into the &kolourpaint; editing area."
msgid ""
"Using the opened dialog you can change <guilabel>Screenshot Delay</guilabel> "
"(in seconds), and choose to <guilabel>Hide Main Window</guilabel> during "
"screenshotting. When you are ready to take a screenshot just click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>. The screenshot taken will be placed directly into "
"the &kolourpaint; editing area."
msgstr ""
"Koristeći otvoreni dijalog možete promijeniti <guilabel> Odgoda Screenshota "
"</guilabel> (u sekundama), i izabrati <guilabel>Sakrij Glavni Prozor </"
"guilabel> u toku screenshota. Kada ste spremni da uslikate screenshot samo "
"kliknite <guibutton> OK </guibutton>. Uslikani screenshot će biti smješten "
"direktno u &kolourpaint; prostor za uređivanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tool Reference"
msgstr "Referenca na alat"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A quick way to select a tool in &kolourpaint; is to press the single key "
"shortcut associated with it, documented below and in the <interface>Tool "
"Box</interface> tooltips. You can also hold <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"&Shift;</keycombo> while pressing the key, which is necessary when you are "
"writing text (as the single key shortcuts will be disabled). For example, to "
"select the brush, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo> or just B (when not writing text)."
msgstr ""
"Brzi način da označite alat u &kolourpaint;-u je da pritisnete jednu tipku "
"koja je povezana sa tim alatom, dokumentirano ispod i u <interface> Kutija "
"Alata </interface> pomoć za alate. Možete također držati tipke <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;</keycombo> dok pritišćete dugme, što je "
"potrebno kada pišete tekst (budući da će kratice sa jednom tipkom biti "
"onemogućene). Naprimjer, da biste odabrali četku, pritisnite <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> ili samo B (kada "
"ne pišete tekst)."

