#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brush"
msgstr "Četka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click or click and drag with the brush to draw."
msgstr "Kliknite i povucite sa četkom da crtate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the shapes to select the brush shape. You can use a "
"circular, square, slash or backslash brush shape."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na neki od oblika da selektujete oblik četke. Možete koristiti "
"okruglu, kockastu, četka u obliku kose crte nadesno i nalijevo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:431 index.docbook:484 index.docbook:619 index.docbook:671
#: index.docbook:809
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; draws in the foreground color. The &RMB; draws in the background "
"color."
msgstr "&LMB; crta u prednjoj boji. &RMB; crta u pozadinskoj boji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Picker"
msgstr "Izabirač boja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the foreground color, <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click on a "
"pixel. To set the background color, <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click "
"on a pixel. &kolourpaint; will then return to the previously selected tool."
msgstr ""
"Da odaberete prednju boju, <mousebutton>lijevi</mousebutton> klik na "
"piksel.  Da biste odabrali pozadinsku boju, <mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> "
"klik na piksel. &kolourpaint; će se zatim vratiti na prethodno selektovani "
"alat."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connected Lines and Polygon"
msgstr "Povezane linije i mnogougao"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to draw connected lines. The polygon tool is used in the same "
"way, however, the start and end points are automatically connected to form a "
"polygon."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i povucite da crtate povezane linije. Alat za mnogougao se koristi "
"na isti način, samo što se početna i krajnja tačka automatski povežu da "
"naprave mnogougao."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; draws in the foreground color. The &RMB; draws in the background "
"color, and will also reverse the fill color for polygons."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; crta u prednjoj boji. &RMB; crta u pozadinskoj boji, i također će "
"vratiti boju punjenja mnogougla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the line width</link>. For "
"polygons, you can also <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the fill style</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Možete <link linkend=\"tool-options\">postaviti širinu linije</link>. Za "
"mnogouglove, također možete <link linkend=\"tool-options\">postaviti stil "
"punjenja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Curve"
msgstr "Kriva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to draw a line - this sets the start and end points. You can "
"set up to two control points by dragging. To finish the curve without using "
"both or any control points, click the other mouse button. The curve tool "
"draws a Cubic Bezier."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i povucite da nacrtate liniju - ovo postavlja početnu i krajnju "
"tačku. Možete staviti do dvije kontrolne tačke povlačenjem. Da završite "
"krivu bez korištenja obe ili ijedne konstrolne tačke, kliknite drugo dugme "
"miša. Alat za crtanje krivih linija crta Cubic Bezier krivu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:487 index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can also <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the line width</link>."
msgstr ""
"Također možete <link linkend=\"tool-options\">postaviti širinu linije</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ellipse"
msgstr "Elipsa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag to draw an ellipse."
msgstr "Kliknite i povucite da biste nacrtali elipsu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:502 index.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; draws in the foreground color. The &RMB; draws in the background "
"color, and will reverse the fill color."
msgstr ""
"&LMB; crta u prednjoj boji. &RMB; crta u pozadinskoj boji i povratit će boju "
"punjenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:505 index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also <link linkend=\"tool-options\">set the line width and fill "
"style</link>."
msgstr ""
"Također možete <link linkend=\"tool-options\">podesiti širinu i stil "
"punjenja</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:508 index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid "For additional functionality, use the modifier keys:"
msgstr "Za dodatne funkcionalnost, koristite tipke za modificiranje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold &Shift; and drag to draw a circle."
msgstr "Pritisnite &Shift; i povucite da nacrtate krug."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw an ellipse with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl;, click on "
"the center point, and drag until the ellipse is the correct size and shape."
msgstr ""
"Da biste nacrtali elipsu sa centralnom tačkom po izboru, držite &Ctrl;, "
"kliknite na centralnu tačku i povucite dok elipsa nije korektne veličine i "
"oblika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a circle with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl; and "
"&Shift;, click on the center point, and drag until the circle is the correct "
"size."
msgstr ""
"Da biste nacrtali krug sa centralnom tačkom po izboru, držite &Ctrl;, "
"kliknite na centralnu tačku i povucite dok krug nije korektne veličine i "
"oblika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Erasers"
msgstr "Gumice za brisanje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eraser"
msgstr "Gumica za brisanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag with the eraser to rub out mistakes."
msgstr "Kliknite i povucite gumicu da obrišete greške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlike other tools, the erasers draw in the background color. To draw in the "
"foreground color, use the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Za razliku od ostalih alata, gumice za brisanje crtaju u pozadinskoj boji. "
"Da biste crtali u prednjoj boji, koristite &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The eraser only has <link linkend=\"tool-options\">square shapes</link>. To "
"draw with other shapes such as circles use the <link linkend=\"tool-brush"
"\">Brush</link> and the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Gumica za brisanje samo ima <link linkend=\"tool-options\">kvadratne oblike</"
"link>. Da biste nacrtali druge oblike kao npr krugove koristite <link "
"linkend=\"tool-brush\">Četku</link> i &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on the Eraser icon to clear the entire image. This is "
"equivalent to using the <link linkend=\"image-clear\">Clear</link> option on "
"the Image menu."
msgstr ""
"Dupli klik na gumicu za brisanje za čišćenje čitave slike. Ovo je "
"ekvivalentno korištenju <link linkend=\"image-clear\">Očisti</link> opcije "
"na meniju Slika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Eraser"
msgstr "Gumica za brisanje u boji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to replace pixels of the foreground color with the background "
"color. To replace all pixels similar (but not necessarily exactly equal) to "
"the foreground color, such as in dithered images and photos, use a <link "
"linkend=\"color-box\">Color Similarity</link> setting other than Exact."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i povucite da zamijenite piksele prednje boje sa pozadinskom bojom. "
"Da zamijenite sve piksele slične (ali ne nužno iste) prednjoj boji, npr. u "
"slikama i fotografijama sa podrhtavanjem, koristite <link linkend=\"color-box"
"\">Sličnost boja</link> opciju radije nego Egzaktno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unlike other tools, the erasers draw in the background color. To replace "
"pixels of the background color with the foreground color, use the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Za razliku od ostalih alata, gumice za brisanje crtaju u pozadinskoj boji. "
"Da biste zamijenili piksele pozadinske boje sa prednjom bojom, koristite "
"&RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the <link linkend=\"tool-options\">eraser size</link>."
msgstr ""
"Možete konfigurisati <link linkend=\"tool-options\">veličinu gumice za "
"brisanje</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Double-click on the Color Eraser icon to apply it to the entire image."
msgstr "Dupli klik na ikonu za brisanje boje da se primijeni na čitavu sliku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flood Fill"
msgstr "Popunjavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click to fill a region. To fill a dithered region, use a <link linkend="
"\"color-box\">Color Similarity</link> setting other than Exact."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite da popunite regiju. Da popunite regiju sa podrhtavanjem, koristite "
"<link linkend=\"color-box\">Sličnost boje</link> opciju radije nego tačnu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &LMB; fills in the foreground color. The &RMB; fills in the background "
"color."
msgstr "&LMB; popunjava prednjom bojom. &RMB; popunjava pozadinskom bojom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line"
msgstr "Linija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click and drag to draw a line."
msgstr "Kliknite i povucite da nacrtate liniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold &Ctrl; to draw lines angled at the nearest multiple of 30 degrees - "
"these are the lines in the red diagram."
msgstr ""
"Držite &Ctrl; da nacrtate linije pod uglom koji je najbliži umnožak 30 "
"stepeni - ovo su linije na crvenom dijagramu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold &Shift; to draw lines angled at the nearest multiple of 45 degrees - "
"these are the lines in the blue diagram."
msgstr ""
"Držite &Shift; da crtate linije pod uglom koji je najbliži umnožak 45 "
"stepeni - ovo su linije na plavom dijagramu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hold &Ctrl; and &Shift; to draw lines angled at the nearest multiple of 30 "
"or 45 degrees - these are the lines in the green diagram."
msgstr ""
"Držite &Ctrl; i &Shift; da crtate linije pod uglom koji je najbliži umnožak "
"30 ili 45 stepeni - ovo su linije na zelenom dijagramu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Pen</title>"
msgstr "<title>Olovka</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click to draw a dot or click and drag to draw a freehand line."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite da nacrtate tačku ili kliknite i držite da nacrtate liniju "
"slobodnom rukom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rectangles"
msgstr "Pravougaonici"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to draw a rectangle. The Rounded Rectangle is a Rectangle "
"with rounded corners."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i držite da nacrtate pravougaonik. Zaobljeni pravougaonik je "
"pravougaonik sa zaobljenim uglovima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hold &Shift; and drag to draw a square."
msgstr "Držite &Shift; i povucite da nacrtate kocku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a rectangle with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl;, click "
"on the center point, and drag until the rectangle is the correct size and "
"shape."
msgstr ""
"Da biste nacrtali pravougaonik sa centralnom tačkom po izboru, držite "
"&Ctrl;, kliknite na centralnu tačku, i vucite dok pravougaonik nije željene "
"veličine i oblika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To draw a square with a center point of your choice, hold &Ctrl; and "
"&Shift;, click on the center point, and drag until the square is the correct "
"size."
msgstr ""
"Da biste nacrtali kvadrat sa centralnom tačkom po izboru, držite &Ctrl; i "
"&Shift;, kliknite na centralnu tačku, i vucite dok kvadrat nije željene "
"veličine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selections"
msgstr "Selekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the selection tools to draw out the boundary of a selection."
msgstr "Koristite alat za selektovanje da crtate van granica selekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move the selection, click and drag on it. The main view will scroll as "
"required to allow you to move the selection to part of the image that is not "
"currently displayed."
msgstr ""
"Da biste pomjerili selekciju, kliknite na nju i povucite je. Glavni pogled "
"će se pomjerati ukoliko je potrebno da biste pomjerili selekciju na dio "
"slike koji ne može biti prikazan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can free-form <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resize</link> the "
"entire image or <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Smooth Scale</link> the "
"selection using the corresponding handles. Hold &Shift; while free-form "
"scaling the selection to maintain aspect ratio. The &RMB; invokes a context "
"menu with common <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> commands and <link linkend=\"image-"
"effects-section\">Image Effects</link>."
msgstr ""
"Možete ručno <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Promijeni veličinu</link> "
"cijele slike ili <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Glatko skalirati</"
"link> selekciju koristeći odgovarajuće alate. Držite &Shift; dok slobodno "
"skalirate selekciju da zadržite omjer. &RMB; poziva kontekstni meni sa "
"uobičajenim <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> komandama i <link linkend=\"image-"
"effects-section\">Efekti slike</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the cursor keys while drawing out the boundary of the selection "
"or while moving it."
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti tipke kursora dok crtate van granica selekcije ili dok je "
"pomjerate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you hold &Ctrl; before moving the selection, then you will move a copy of "
"it. The selection will be smeared when moving it while &Shift; is held."
msgstr ""
"Ako držite &Ctrl; prije pomjeranja selekcije, tada ćete pomjeriti njenu "
"kopiju. Selekcija će biti zamazana ako držite &Shift; dok je pomjerate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two selection modes: Opaque (default) and Transparent. If you use "
"the Transparent selection mode, all pixels of the background color will be "
"transparent (background subtraction). This allows you to paste a selection "
"without the background. To perform background subtraction on a dithered "
"image, use a <link linkend=\"color-box\">Color Similarity</link> setting "
"other than Exact."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can apply Image Effects to a selection - see the <link linkend=\"image-"
"effects-section\">Image Effects</link> section for more information."
msgstr ""
"Možete primijeniti efekte slike na selekciju - pogledajte <link linkend="
"\"image-effects-section\">Efekti slike</link> odjeljak za više informacija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to save selection to file using the <guimenuitem>Copy to "
"File...</guimenuitem> item from the selection context menu or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy to File...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> item from the main menu."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spraycan"
msgstr "Sprej"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag to spray graffiti. Hold down the mouse button for a more "
"concentrated spray."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i povucite da koristite sprej. Držite dugme miša za više "
"koncentrisan sprej."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the shapes to select the spray size. You can select from "
"spray sizes of 9x9, 17x17 and 29x29."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na jedan od oblika da izaberete veličinu spreja. Možete izabrati "
"između veličina 9x9, 17x17 i 29x29."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:815
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Tekst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click and drag an area in which to write text. As soon as the border will be "
"shown you can start writing the text. Click and drag on the border to move "
"it. You can resize the text box by dragging on the handles or by using the "
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resize</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite i povucite u dio gdje želite pisati tekst. Čim se prikaže granica, "
"možete početi pisati tekst. Kliknite i povucite na granici da ga pomjerite. "
"Možete promijeniti veličinu kutije teksta tako što povučete sa strane ili "
"koristeći <link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Promijeni veličinu </link> "
"dijalog."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have deselected a text box you can use <guimenuitem>Undo</"
"guimenuitem> to edit the text again."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste deselektirali kutiju teksta možete <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> "
"da uredite tekst opet."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Transparent Color"
msgstr "Korištenje providne boje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left picture shows the example image. The right picture shows the "
"addition of text with opaque foreground and background colors."
msgstr ""
"Lijeva slika pokazuje primjer slike. Desna slika prikazuje dodatak teksta sa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left picture shows the addition of text with opaque foreground colors "
"and a transparent background color. The right picture shows the addition of "
"text with a transparent foreground color and opaque background color."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &LMB; zooms in. The &RMB; zooms out."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag with &LMB; to zoom into a specific area."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Double-click on the Color Eraser icon to apply it to the entire image."
msgid "Double click on the Zoom tool icon to set zoom to \"Fit to Page\"."
msgstr "Dupli klik na ikonu za brisanje boje da se primijeni na čitavu sliku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Tool Options"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the squares to select the eraser size. You can select from "
"squares of side length 2, 3, 5, 9, 17 and 29 pixels."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:899
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The eraser size setting affects the <link linkend=\"tool-erasers\">Erasers</"
"link>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the lines to select the line width. You can select from line "
"widths of 1, 2, 3, 5 and 8 pixel(s)."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na jednu od linija da odaberete širinu linije. Možete odabrati "
"širinu od 1,2,3,5 i 8 piksela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The line width setting affects the <link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Connected "
"Lines</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-curve\">Curve</link>, <link linkend="
"\"tool-ellipse\">Ellipse</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-line\">Line</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Polygon</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-"
"rectangles\">Rectangle</link> and <link linkend=\"tool-rectangles\">Rounded "
"Rectangle</link> tools."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on one of the rectangles to select the fill style. You can select from "
"No Fill, Fill with Background Color and Fill with Foreground Color."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The fill style setting affects the <link linkend=\"tool-ellipse\">Ellipse</"
"link>, <link linkend=\"tool-polystar\">Polygon</link>, <link linkend=\"tool-"
"rectangles\">Rectangle</link> and <link linkend=\"tool-rectangles\">Rounded "
"Rectangle</link> tools."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Working with Color</title>"
msgstr "<title>Rad s bojama</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Color Box"
msgstr "Kutija boja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Box"
msgstr "Kutija boja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Color Box has 3 main sections: the Color Tablet, the Color Palette and "
"the Color Similarity Selector."
msgstr ""
"Kutija s bojama ima 3 glavne sekcije: tablet s bojama, paletu s bojama i "
"selektor sličnih boja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Color Tablet shows the current foreground color as a square on top of "
"another square representing the current background color. When drawing with "
"the &LMB;, the foreground color is used, and when drawing with the &RMB; the "
"background color is used (except for the <link linkend=\"tool-erasers"
"\">Erasers</link>). You can click on the double-ended arrow to swap the "
"foreground and background colors."
msgstr ""
"Tablet s bojama prikazuje trenutnu prednju boju kao kocku na vrhu druge "
"kocke koja predstavlja trenutnu pozadinsku boju. Kada crtate sa &LMD;, "
"prednja boja se koristi, a kada crtate sa &RMB; pozadinska boja se koristi "
"(osim za <link linkend=\"tool-erasers\">Gumicu za brisanje</link>).Možete "
"kliknuti na dvostranu strelicu da zamijenite pozadinsku i prednju boju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Color Palette shows a selection of colors for you to choose from. The "
"translucent pyramid represents the transparent color. Left-click on a color "
"to set the foreground color and right-click on a color to set the background "
"color. You can also drag and drop any opaque color into the Color Tablet "
"squares. To edit a color in the Color Tablet or Palette, double-click on it. "
"The <link linkend=\"tool-color-picker\">Color Picker</link> tool allows you "
"to select a color from the image."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Color Similarity allows you to work more effectively with dithered images "
"and photos, in a comparable manner to the <quote>Magic Wand</quote> feature "
"of other paint programs. It applies to transparent selections, as well as "
"the <link linkend=\"tool-flood-fill\">Flood Fill</link>, <link linkend="
"\"tool-eraser-clr\">Color Eraser</link> and <link linkend=\"image-autocrop"
"\">Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</link> tools. Double-click on the Color "
"Similarity Selector to choose how similar colors must be to be considered "
"identical. When using selections in Transparent mode, any color in the "
"selection that is similar to the background color will also be made "
"transparent."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left picture shows the example image. The right pictures demonstrate the "
"use of a flood fill, with Color Similarity settings of 5%, 15% and 30%. In "
"this example, with a Color Similarity setting of <guilabel>Exact</guilabel>, "
"a flood fill at (80, 100) would only fill one pixel, as the surrounding "
"pixels are similar but not identical. As Color Similarity is increased, more "
"pixels that are similar in color are considered identical, hence the fill "
"extends further."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>View Options</title>"
msgstr "<title>Pogledaj opcije</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Options Reference"
msgstr "Pogledaj reference na opcije"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"view-zoom\">Zoom incorporating the Grid</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"view-zoom\">Inkorporiranje zooma u mrežu</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"view-thumbnail\">Thumbnail</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"view-thumbnail\">Sličice</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Zoom incorporating the Grid</title>"
msgstr "<title>Inkorporiranje zooma u mrežu</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Increase the zoom level to edit images with more precision, or reduce it to "
"see more of the image."
msgstr ""
"Povećavanje nivoa zooma da se slike uređuju preciznije, ili reduciranje "
"istog da se vidi veći dio slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At zoom levels that aren't multiples of 100%, parts of the image may appear "
"to move when the user interacts with it. Other minor redraw glitches may "
"also occur at such zoom levels."
msgstr ""
"Na zoomu koji nije umnožak 100%, može se činiti da se dijelovi slike miču "
"kada korisnik radi sa njima. Druge manje greške se također mogu pojaviti na "
"takvim nivoima zumiranja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At zoom levels of 400% or greater that are also multiples of 100%, you can "
"<guimenuitem>Show Grid</guimenuitem> to more accurately edit individual "
"pixels."
msgstr ""
"Na nivoima zooma većim ili jednakim 400% koji su također umnošci 100%, "
"možete koristiti <guimenuitem>Prikaži mrežu</guimenuitem> da preciznije "
"uređujete individualne piksele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first picture shows the <link linkend=\"tool-text\">Text</link> tool "
"icon, while the latter shows it at 600% zoom with the grid on."
msgstr ""
"Prva slika prikazuje <link linkend=\"tool-text\">Tekst</link> ikonu alata, "
"dok ga druga prikazuje 600% uvećan sa uključenom mrežom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way of zooming when not drawing is to scroll the <mousebutton>wheel</"
"mousebutton> while holding &Ctrl;."
msgstr ""
"Drugi način zumiranja kada ne crtate je skrolanje <mousebutton> točkića </"
"mousebutton> dok držite &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Thumbnail</title>"
msgstr "<title>Sličice</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guimenuitem>Zoomed Thumbnail Mode</guimenuitem> is selected, the entire "
"image is displayed, scaled as required to fit the thumbnail window (top-"
"right picture)."
msgstr ""
"Ako je <guimenuitem>Režim uvećanog thumbnail-a</guimenuitem> selektovan, "
"čitava slika je prikazana, skalirana kako je potrebno da se uklopi u prozor "
"za thumbnail (gornja desna slika)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Otherwise, the thumbnail displays as much of the image as possible, starting "
"from the top-left of the main view (bottom-right picture)."
msgstr ""
"U suprotnom, thumbnail prikazuje najveći mogući dio slike, počevši od "
"gornjeg lijevog dijela glavnog pogleda (donja desna slika)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Image Effects</title>"
msgstr "<title>Efekti Slike</title>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Effects Reference"
msgstr "Referenca na efekte slike"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-autocrop\">Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-autocrop\">Automatsko izrezivanje/Skloni internu "
"granicu</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balance</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balans</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-clear\">Clear</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-clear\">Očisti </link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1085
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Emboss</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Naglasi</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1086
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-flatten\">Flatten</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-flatten\">Izravnaj</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-flip\">Flip (upside down)</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-flip\">Okreni (naopako)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1088
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invert</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invertuj</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1089
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Reduce Colors</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Smanji Boje</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-grayscale\">Reduce to Grayscale</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-grayscale\">Reduciraj na nijanse sive</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Reduciraj Monohromatski (sa "
"podrhtavanjem)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-mirror\">Mirror (horizontally)</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-mirror\">Ogledalo (horizontalno)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1093
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resize / Scale</link>"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Promijeni veličinu / Skaliraj</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotate</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotiraj</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-set-as-image\">Set as Image (Crop)</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-set-as-image\">Postavi kao sliku (izreži)</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-skew\">Skew</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-skew\">Iskrivi </link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-soften-sharpen\">Soften &amp; Sharpen</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-soften-sharpen\">Smekšaj &amp; Izoštri</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-more-effects\">More Effects</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-more-effects\">Više efekata</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:1099
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"image-notes\">Bilješke</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Autocrop / Remove Internal Border</title>"
msgstr "<title>Automatsko izrezivanje / Skloni internu granicu</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This automatically removes the border of an image or selection. Use Autocrop "
"if you have a figure that does not fill the entire image or selection and "
"you wish to remove the excess whitespace. To use this feature with a "
"dithered image border, you will also need to use <link linkend=\"color-box"
"\">Color Similarity</link>."
msgstr ""
"Automatski sklanja granicu slike ili selekcije. Koristite Autocrop ako imate "
"figuru koja ne popunjava čitavu selekciju ili sliku i želite skloniti bijeli "
"prostor koji je viška. Da biste koristili ovu opciju sa granicom slike sa "
"podrhtavanjem, također ćete trebati koristiti <link linkend=\"color-box"
"\">Sličnost boja</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Balance</title>"
msgstr "<title>Balansiraj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1116 index.docbook:1154 index.docbook:1174 index.docbook:1200
#: index.docbook:1234 index.docbook:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature is accessible from the <link linkend=\"image-more-effects"
"\">More Effects</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ova opcija je pristupačna preko dijaloga <link linkend=\"image-more-effects"
"\">Više efekata</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to set the brightness, contrast and gamma of the image or "
"selection."
msgstr "Omogućava da podesite svjetlinu, kontrast i gama slike ili selekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more common measure of gamma (a decimal from 0.10 to 10.00) is located "
"between the <guilabel>Gamma</guilabel> spinbox and the <guibutton>Reset</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Više uobičajena mjera game (decimani broj od 0.10 do 10.00) je locirana "
"između <guilabel>Gamma</guilabel> spinox i <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> "
"dugme."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Clear</title>"
msgstr "<title>Očisti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid "This fills the entire image or selection with the background color."
msgstr "Popunjava čitavu sliku ili selekciju pozadinskom bojom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click on the <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-std\">Eraser</link> icon to "
"clear the entire image."
msgstr ""
"Dupli klik na <link linkend=\"tool-eraser-std\">Gumicu za brisanje</link> "
"ikonu da biste očistili čitavu sliku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Emboss</title>"
msgstr "<title>Istaknuti</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check <guilabel>Enable</guilabel> to apply the Emboss effect. This "
"emphasises the edges and gives the image or selection an &quot;engraved "
"look&quot;."
msgstr ""
"Označite <guilabel>Omogući</guilabel> da biste primijenili efekat za "
"isticanje. Ovo naglašava ivice i daje slici ili selekciji &quot; urezani "
"izgled &quot;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Flatten</title>"
msgstr "<title>Izravnaj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "This recolors the image with varying shades of the two selected colors."
msgstr "Boji sliku sa različitim nijansama dvije izabrane boje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Flip (upside down)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Okreni (naopako)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid "This flips the entire image or selection vertically."
msgstr "Okreće čitavu sliku ili selekciju vertikalno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Invert</title>"
msgstr "<title>Invertuj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to invert one or more RGB channels in the image or "
"selection. Select <guilabel>All</guilabel> to change a photo into a negative "
"and vice versa. This generally looks quite funny."
msgstr ""
"Omogućava da invertujete jedan ili više RGB kanala slike ili selekcije. "
"Označite <guilabel> Sve </guilabel> da biste promijenili sliku u negativ i "
"obrnuto. Ovo generalno izgleda poprilično smiješno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To quickly invert all channels, you do not need to use this dialog. You can "
"instead access the <guimenuitem>Invert Colors</guimenuitem> item in the "
"<guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu. The "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> item is only displayed in the menubar if you "
"use one of the selection tools. Additionally you can reach this action from "
"the context menu opened with a &RMB; click in the image area."
msgstr ""
"Da biste brzo invertovali sve kanale, ne morate koristiti ovaj dijalog. "
"Umjesto toga možete pristupiti <guimenuitem>Invertuj boje</"
"guimenuitem>stavki u <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> ili <guimenu>Selekcija</"
"guimenu> meniju. Stavka <guimenu>Selekcija</guimenu> je samo prikazana u "
"traci menija ako koristite jedan od alata za selektovanje. Dodatno možete "
"doći do ove akcije iz kontekstnog menija koji se otvara &RMB; klikom na "
"područje slike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Mirror (horizontally)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Ogledalo (horizontalno)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid "This mirrors the entire image or selection horizontally."
msgstr "Preslikava čitavu sliku ili selekciju horizontalno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce Colors</title>"
msgstr "<title>Smanji Boje</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This reduces the number of colors used by the image or selection, with or "
"without dithering."
msgstr ""
"Reducira broj boja koje slika ili selekcija koristi, sa ili bez podrhtavanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Dithering generally provides better quality results, however, you may wish "
"to disable it for artistic effects; &eg; using <guilabel>Monochrome</"
"guilabel> instead of <guilabel>Monochrome (Dithered)</guilabel> gives a "
"silhouette effect."
msgstr ""
"Podrhvatanje generalno obezbjeđuje rezultate bolje kvalitete, ali možta ga "
"ipak želite isključiti radi umjetničkih efekata; &eg; koristeći <guilabel> "
"Monohromatski </guilabel> umjesto <guilabel> Monohromatski (sa "
"podrhtavanjem) </guilabel> će dati efekat siluete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another important distinction is that while <guilabel>Monochrome (Dithered)</"
"guilabel> will always reduce the entire image or selection to black and "
"white, <guilabel>Monochrome</guilabel> will do this only if the image or "
"selection contains more than 2 colors."
msgstr ""
"Još jedna važna razlika je to da dok <guilabel> Monohromatski (sa "
"podrhtavanjem) </guilabel> će uvijek reducirati čitavu sliku ili selekciju "
"na crno-bijelo,  <guilabel> Monohromatski </guilabel> će ovo uraditi samo "
"ako slika ili selekcija ima više od 2 boje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a quick, dithered monochrome image or selection, use the <link linkend="
"\"image-monochrome\">Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</link> item of the "
"<guimenu>Image</guimenu> or <guimenu>Selection</guimenu> menu. The "
"<guimenu>Selection</guimenu> item is only displayed in the menubar if you "
"use one of the selection tools. Additionally you can reach this action from "
"the context menu opened with a &RMB; click in the image area."
msgstr ""
"Za brzu, monohromatsku sliku ili selekciju sa podrhtavanjem, koristite <link "
"linkend=\"image-monochrome\">Reduciraj monohromatski (sa podrhtavnjem) </"
"link> stavku sa <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> ili  <guimenu>Selekcija</guimenu> "
"menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the number of colors here has no effect on the color depth of the "
"file format. If you want to change the color depth, you should select it in "
"the file saving dialogs. Note that, confusingly, changing the color depth "
"also changes the number of colors."
msgstr ""
"Promjena broja boja ovdje nema efekta na dubinu boje formata fajla. Ako "
"želite promijeniti dubinu boje, trebate je selektovati u dijalogu za "
"snimanje fajlove. Imajte na umu da, iako zbunjujuće, promjena dubine boje "
"također mijenja broj boja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce to Grayscale</title>"
msgstr "<title>Reduciraj na sivo</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "This reduces the entire image or selection to grayscale."
msgstr "Reducira čitavu sliku ili selekciju da bude u nijansama sive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Reduce to Monochrome (Dithered)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Reduciraj na monohromatski (sa podrhtavanjem)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid "This reduces the entire image or selection to black and white."
msgstr "Čitavu selekciju mijenja u crno-bijelo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want the image or selection to be dithered, use the <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\"> Reduce Colors</link> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ako ne želite da slika ili selekcija podrhtavaju, koristite <link linkend="
"\"image-reduce-colors\">Smanji boje</link> dijalog."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Resize / Scale</title>"
msgstr "<title>Promijeni veličinu / Skaliraj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Resizing the image changes the dimensions of the image without applying a "
"transformation to the existing contents. Scaling the image will stretch the "
"existing contents to the new dimensions. <guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> "
"generally provides better quality results than Scaling, by blending "
"neighbouring colors."
msgstr ""
"Promjena veličine slike mijenja dimenzije slike bez primjene transformacije "
"na postojećem sadržaju. Skaliranje slike će razvući postojeći sadržaj na "
"nove dimenzije. <guibutton> Neprekidna Skala </guibutton> generalno "
"omogućava rezultate bolje kvalitete nego skaliranje, tako što miješa "
"susjedne boje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can express the new dimensions in pixels, or as a percentage of the "
"original size. If you select <guilabel>Keep aspect ratio</guilabel>, the "
"width and height will be scaled by the same percentage."
msgstr ""
"Možete izraziti nove dimenzije u pikselima, ili kao procenat originalne "
"veličine. Ako odaberete <guilabel> Održi omjer aspekta </guilabel>, širina i "
"visina će biti skalirane za isti procenat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can free-form <guibutton>Resize</guibutton> the entire image or "
"<guibutton>Smooth Scale</guibutton> the selection using the corresponding "
"handles."
msgstr ""
"Možete slobodno <guibutton>Raširiti</guibutton> cijelu sliku ili "
"<guibutton>Glatko skalirati</guibutton> izbor uz pomoć odgovarajućih držača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only scaling is supported for selections, and only resizing is supported for "
"text boxes. See <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link> for additional "
"details about applying these effects."
msgstr ""
"Samo skaliranje je podržano za selekcije, i samo promjena veličine je "
"podržana za kutije teksta. Pogledajte <link linkend=\"image-notes"
"\">Bilješke</link> za dodatne detalje o primjeni ovih efekata."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Rotate</title>"
msgstr "<title>Rotiraj</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rotates the image. You can specify the angle and direction of rotation."
msgstr "Rotira sliku. Možete specificirati ugao i smjer rotacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reverse the direction of rotation by specifying a negative custom "
"angle."
msgstr "Možete obrnuti smjer rotacije tako što specificirate negativan ugao."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1348 index.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <link linkend=\"image-notes\">Notes</link> for details about applying "
"this effect to a selection."
msgstr ""
"Vidi <link linkend=\"image-notes\">bilješke</link> za detalje o primjeni "
"ovih efekata na selekcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Set as Image (Crop)</title>"
msgstr "<title>Postavi kao sliku (Izreži)</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will set the selection as the image."
msgstr "Ovim postavljate selektovano kao sliku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is only available when you have an active selection."
msgstr "Ovo je moguće samo kad imate aktivnu selekciju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1365
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Skew</title>"
msgstr "<title>Iskrivi</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This skews the entire image or selection horizontally and/or vertically."
msgstr "Iskrivljava čitavu sliku horizontalno ili vertikalno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Soften &amp; Sharpen</title>"
msgstr "<title>Smekšaj &amp; Izoštri</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use this effect to soften or sharpen the image."
msgstr "Koristite ovaj efekat da omekšate ili izoštrite sliku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>More Effects</title>"
msgstr "<title>Više efekata</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog contains the <link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balance</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-emboss\">Emboss</link>, <link linkend=\"image-flatten"
"\">Flatten</link>, <link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invert</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Reduce Colors</link> and <link linkend="
"\"image-soften-sharpen\">Soften &amp; Sharpen</link> features."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj dijalog sadrži <link linkend=\"image-balance\">Balans</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-emboss\">Isticanje</link>, <link linkend=\"image-flatten"
"\">Poravnavanje</link>, <link linkend=\"image-invert\">Invertovanje</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-reduce-colors\">Redukcija boja</link> and <link "
"linkend=\"image-soften-sharpen\">Smekšaj &amp; Izoštri</link> opcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1417
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Notes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Bilješke</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Resizing / Scaling</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotating</link> and <link linkend=\"image-skew"
"\">Skewing</link> may change the dimensions of the image. You can view the "
"new dimensions in the dialog."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"image-resize-scale\">Promjena veličine/skaliranje</link>, "
"<link linkend=\"image-rotate\">Rotiranje</link> and <link linkend=\"image-"
"skew\">Iskrivljavanje</link> mogu promijeniti dimenzije slike. Možete "
"vidjeti nove dimenzije u dijalogu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you apply these effects to an image, the image will be resized if "
"necessary. However, if you apply these effects to a selection, the image "
"will not be resized, even if the transformed selection does not fit."
msgstr ""
"Ako primijenite ove efekte na sliku, veličina slike će po potrebi biti "
"promijenjena. Kako god, ako primijenite ove efekte na selekciju, veličina "
"slike neće biti promijenjena, iako se transformisana selekcija ne uklapa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left image has been rotated 30 degrees clockwise to form the right "
"image. &kolourpaint; has automatically enlarged the image to accommodate the "
"larger contents."
msgstr ""
"Lijeva slika je rotirana 30 stepeni u smjeru kazaljke na satu da se formira "
"desna slika. &kolourpaint; je automatski povećao sliku da zadovolji veće "
"sadržaje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left <emphasis>selection</emphasis> has been rotated 30 degrees "
"clockwise to form the right selection. The image size has remained the same, "
"hence parts of the selection will not be visible without <link linkend="
"\"image-resize-scale\">Resizing</link> the <emphasis>image</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Lijeva<emphasis>selekcija</emphasis> je zarotirana 30 stepeni u smjeru "
"kazaljke na satu da se napravi desna selekcija. Veličina slike je ostala "
"ista, tako da dijelovi selekcije neće biti vidljivi bez <link linkend="
"\"image-resize-scale\">Promjena</link> veličine <emphasis>slike</emphasis>."

